latestIgtvVideos.title: How to Make a Cookie Musubi
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here's a good way to get your daily serving of fruit into your diet. Check out this twist on the local favorite: the Spam musubi. Prepare everything the same as usual, but use a Mango Macadamia cookie instead of Spam. Be sure to brush on a mixture of shoyu (soy sauce) and sugar.
